{
    "publish_date": "2014-04-03T05:16:19.000Z", 
    "video_length": "PT17M48S", 
    "captions": [
        {
            "text": "Here&#39;s the deal:", 
            "dur": "1.55", 
            "start": "14.808"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Life is really all about love.", 
            "dur": "6.315", 
            "start": "16.968"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I&#39;m not just saying that\nbecause I&#39;m a father of a newborn baby;", 
            "dur": "4.059", 
            "start": "24.453"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I&#39;m saying that because\nas a teacher and as a therapist", 
            "dur": "5.196", 
            "start": "28.512"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I&#39;ve seen people basically\nchoose between two things:", 
            "dur": "4.063", 
            "start": "33.708"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "love or something else.", 
            "dur": "3.785", 
            "start": "38.361"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "What I&#39;ve witnessed\nand experienced is this:", 
            "dur": "3.368", 
            "start": "43.633"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "When people choose love,", 
            "dur": "2.737", 
            "start": "47.001"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "they always choose right.", 
            "dur": "2.616", 
            "start": "49.738"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I was asked to speak today\non the topic of illumination,", 
            "dur": "3.579", 
            "start": "53.292"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and it made me think about the way\nthe light inside us all can shine.", 
            "dur": "5.906", 
            "start": "56.871"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "My favorite way is through our love", 
            "dur": "2.573", 
            "start": "63.567"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "which can illuminate in our relationships.", 
            "dur": "3.368", 
            "start": "66.14"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The most important relationship\nthat we&#39;ll ever have,", 
            "dur": "3.219", 
            "start": "70.038"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "is the relationship\nthat we have with ourselves.", 
            "dur": "2.537", 
            "start": "73.257"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And next comes the relationships\nthat we share with one another.", 
            "dur": "5.407", 
            "start": "76.604"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "As simply as I can put it,", 
            "dur": "2.385", 
            "start": "82.651"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "we are here, on this very Earth,\nto love and to be loved -", 
            "dur": "6.764", 
            "start": "85.036"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and love is light.", 
            "dur": "2.459", 
            "start": "92.527"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "In a second, what I&#39;d like \nto do with you today,", 
            "dur": "2.285", 
            "start": "95.496"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "is a brief, relaxing, \nguided-imagery exercise,", 
            "dur": "3.497", 
            "start": "97.781"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "where I&#39;m going to have you\nclose your eyes and consider", 
            "dur": "2.756", 
            "start": "101.278"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "three expressions of light\nthat can return us to love.", 
            "dur": "4.646", 
            "start": "104.034"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I&#39;m going to have you close your eyes\nand consider three items,", 
            "dur": "3.088", 
            "start": "108.68"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and then associate each item\nwith a person in your life.", 
            "dur": "3.878", 
            "start": "111.768"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So, let&#39;s get ready.", 
            "dur": "1.405", 
            "start": "115.646"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Can I ask you to put\nyour feet flat on the floor,", 
            "dur": "3.586", 
            "start": "117.491"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "palms facing up in your lap,", 
            "dur": "3.746", 
            "start": "121.077"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and when you&#39;re ready,", 
            "dur": "1.742", 
            "start": "124.823"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "gently allow your upper eyelids\nto meet your lower eyelashes.", 
            "dur": "4.569", 
            "start": "126.565"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Close your eyes \nand let&#39;s everyone take a deep breath.", 
            "dur": "4.312", 
            "start": "131.134"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Relax your shoulders.", 
            "dur": "2.345", 
            "start": "135.446"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The first item I&#39;d like you\nto picture is the sun.", 
            "dur": "3.85", 
            "start": "137.791"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Picture the sun in the big, blue sky,\nfeel the warmth of her rays,", 
            "dur": "6.231", 
            "start": "141.641"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and consider how the sun\ncontinues to show up every day,", 
            "dur": "4.979", 
            "start": "147.872"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "sharing its light and energy\nunconditionally,", 
            "dur": "4.872", 
            "start": "152.851"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "even on a cold February morning.", 
            "dur": "2.982", 
            "start": "157.723"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Is there somebody in your life\nthat reminds you of the sun?", 
            "dur": "4.074", 
            "start": "161.485"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Somebody that loves you unconditionally?", 
            "dur": "3.409", 
            "start": "165.559"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Picture that person now\nand feel their love.", 
            "dur": "4.672", 
            "start": "168.968"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The next item I&#39;d like you\nto picture is a lighthouse.", 
            "dur": "3.987", 
            "start": "175.55"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "See the light emanating\nfrom the top of the structure", 
            "dur": "3.174", 
            "start": "180.237"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "at the ocean&#39;s edge\nwhere the sea meets the land,", 
            "dur": "4.779", 
            "start": "183.411"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and remember its primary purpose:", 
            "dur": "2.642", 
            "start": "188.19"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "To help guide sailors and boaters home.", 
            "dur": "3.034", 
            "start": "190.832"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Is there somebody in your life\nthat helps guide you home?", 
            "dur": "3.859", 
            "start": "194.766"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "To your authentic self?", 
            "dur": "1.77", 
            "start": "198.625"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "To the truth of who you are?", 
            "dur": "2.111", 
            "start": "200.395"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "To the person that you&#39;re meant to be?", 
            "dur": "2.109", 
            "start": "202.506"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "To the path that you&#39;re meant to be on?", 
            "dur": "2.669", 
            "start": "204.615"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Picture that person now", 
            "dur": "2.331", 
            "start": "207.284"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and consider the direction\nthat they&#39;re encouraging you to head in.", 
            "dur": "3.908", 
            "start": "209.615"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The last item I&#39;d like you\nto picture is a disco ball.", 
            "dur": "4.331", 
            "start": "214.723"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "See the light bouncing off of it,", 
            "dur": "3.697", 
            "start": "219.054"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "think of the energy in the room\nwhere you might find this unique object,", 
            "dur": "4.51", 
            "start": "222.751"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "maybe you hear\nyour favorite song playing.", 
            "dur": "3.044", 
            "start": "227.261"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Is there somebody in your life\nthat reminds you of a disco ball?", 
            "dur": "3.702", 
            "start": "230.765"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Somebody that shows up\nwith the fun, loving energy", 
            "dur": "3.002", 
            "start": "234.467"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "wherever they are, wherever they go?", 
            "dur": "2.897", 
            "start": "237.469"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Picture that person now", 
            "dur": "2.377", 
            "start": "240.366"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and consider how they are encouraging\nyou to live and love.", 
            "dur": "5.811", 
            "start": "242.743"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Gently float open your eyes.", 
            "dur": "2.513", 
            "start": "250.304"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Today I&#39;d like to share a story with you\nabout a student of mine.", 
            "dur": "4.497", 
            "start": "253.967"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "His name was Daniel.", 
            "dur": "1.617", 
            "start": "259.214"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I met Daniel the very first year\nI was a classroom teacher.", 
            "dur": "3.62", 
            "start": "261.981"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I had no experience as a theology teacher\nin an all-boys prep school,", 
            "dur": "5.343", 
            "start": "266.171"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and somehow this little guy,\nthis 103-pound wrestler,", 
            "dur": "6.083", 
            "start": "271.514"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "he became more of a teacher to me\nthan a student,", 
            "dur": "3.968", 
            "start": "277.597"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "because he showed me\nand everybody in the school building", 
            "dur": "2.841", 
            "start": "281.565"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "how to shine their love and their light", 
            "dur": "3.413", 
            "start": "284.406"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "by being an example of how it&#39;s done.", 
            "dur": "2.949", 
            "start": "287.819"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You see, the same year \nthat I met this little guy", 
            "dur": "3.033", 
            "start": "291.548"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "was the same year\nthat I was cut from the NFL.", 
            "dur": "3.179", 
            "start": "294.581"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Felt like a little bit of my light\nhad been taken from me", 
            "dur": "3.75", 
            "start": "297.76"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "when the Baltimore Ravens told me\nI can no longer be their quarterback.", 
            "dur": "4.738", 
            "start": "301.51"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I had trained with them all summer,\nI felt like a kid in Disney,", 
            "dur": "5.005", 
            "start": "306.248"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I was playing and competing\nwith some of my childhood heroes", 
            "dur": "2.818", 
            "start": "311.263"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "in stadiums\nthat I had only visited as a fan.", 
            "dur": "2.962", 
            "start": "314.081"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Playing in the NFL\nwas an incredible experience,", 
            "dur": "4.334", 
            "start": "317.653"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but at the end of the summer,", 
            "dur": "2.136", 
            "start": "321.987"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "a week before our first game,\non the last day of cuts,", 
            "dur": "3.64", 
            "start": "324.123"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I was released.", 
            "dur": "1.398", 
            "start": "327.763"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I had to return home to New Jersey \nto figure out a new career.", 
            "dur": "4.406", 
            "start": "330.031"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I had graduated\nfrom Georgetown University", 
            "dur": "2.147", 
            "start": "335.237"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "with the degree in psychology,\nso I guessed I could teach that,", 
            "dur": "4.827", 
            "start": "337.384"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but I was hired\nat an all-boys prep school", 
            "dur": "2.343", 
            "start": "342.211"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to coach football and teach theology.", 
            "dur": "3.257", 
            "start": "344.554"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It was kind of like a life course\nfor the incoming freshmen.", 
            "dur": "3.188", 
            "start": "348.291"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Gave me the opportunity to teach the guys", 
            "dur": "2.114", 
            "start": "351.479"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the importance of being kind,\ncaring and thoughtful.", 
            "dur": "4.162", 
            "start": "353.593"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It really healed my broken heart.", 
            "dur": "2.658", 
            "start": "358.485"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I loved teaching \nas much as I loved playing football.", 
            "dur": "3.279", 
            "start": "361.143"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And that&#39;s where I met Daniel.", 
            "dur": "1.708", 
            "start": "364.422"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "He came into my classroom\nlike a little disco ball.", 
            "dur": "2.634", 
            "start": "366.13"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "He had an energy and a light about him\nthat everybody wanted to be around.", 
            "dur": "4.848", 
            "start": "369.264"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Daniel connected\nwith everybody in the school.", 
            "dur": "3.004", 
            "start": "374.112"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I used to love watching him\nwalk the hallways.", 
            "dur": "2.73", 
            "start": "377.116"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "His smile was reflected back to him\nin every corner.", 
            "dur": "3.152", 
            "start": "379.846"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Athletes, band guys,\ncool guys, smart guys,", 
            "dur": "4.369", 
            "start": "382.998"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "teachers and coaches,", 
            "dur": "2.089", 
            "start": "387.367"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "all felt the love of this pint-sized,\n103-pound wrestler.", 
            "dur": "3.974", 
            "start": "389.456"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "People loved Daniel because he was free.", 
            "dur": "2.819", 
            "start": "394.36"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "He was free to be himself,", 
            "dur": "2.668", 
            "start": "397.729"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and most of us know\nhow difficult that can be.", 
            "dur": "3.126", 
            "start": "400.397"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I remember when Daniel\nfound out it was my birthday", 
            "dur": "3.7", 
            "start": "404.303"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "during his freshman year.", 
            "dur": "2.088", 
            "start": "408.003"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "He took it upon himself to create\na homemade birthday card for me.", 
            "dur": "3.588", 
            "start": "410.091"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "He even taped a Starburst candy\nand a pack of Wrigley&#39;s gum to the inside.", 
            "dur": "5.739", 
            "start": "413.679"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "He presented it to me\nin front of the class.", 
            "dur": "2.577", 
            "start": "419.418"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Daniel was redefining cool,", 
            "dur": "2.853", 
            "start": "422.515"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and he made it cool\nto be thoughtful, caring and kind,", 
            "dur": "3.707", 
            "start": "425.368"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and his classmates loved him for it.", 
            "dur": "2.342", 
            "start": "429.075"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It was in this way\nthat our brotherly bond began.", 
            "dur": "3.913", 
            "start": "432.047"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And it was during his sophomore year", 
            "dur": "2.078", 
            "start": "435.96"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that Daniel started to campaign\nfor me to date his older cousin Lia,", 
            "dur": "4.271", 
            "start": "438.038"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "so that we could officially be family.", 
            "dur": "2.61", 
            "start": "442.309"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "(Laughter)", 
            "dur": "1.472", 
            "start": "444.919"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "He even brought her\nto a wrestling match one weekend.", 
            "dur": "2.872", 
            "start": "446.391"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I was only there\nwith about one other person,", 
            "dur": "2.69", 
            "start": "449.263"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and Daniel had about 15 relatives\ncheering him on that night.", 
            "dur": "3.643", 
            "start": "451.953"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It was a beautiful night.", 
            "dur": "1.884", 
            "start": "456.576"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Then Daniel came into school\nthe following Monday,", 
            "dur": "2.426", 
            "start": "458.48"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and he was mad.", 
            "dur": "1.307", 
            "start": "460.906"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "He said, &quot;Mr. Ward, you brought\nyour girlfriend to my wrestling match,", 
            "dur": "4.775", 
            "start": "462.873"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "when I brought my cousin\nto introduce you?&quot;", 
            "dur": "2.012", 
            "start": "467.648"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "(Laughter)", 
            "dur": "1.828", 
            "start": "469.66"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I said, &quot;Wow, Daniel, hold on a second!", 
            "dur": "2.54", 
            "start": "471.488"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "That girl happens to be my younger sister,", 
            "dur": "2.54", 
            "start": "474.028"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "(Laughter)", 
            "dur": "1.034", 
            "start": "476.568"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and, second of all,", 
            "dur": "1.052", 
            "start": "477.602"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I didn&#39;t know you were trying\nto play matchmaker that night.&quot;", 
            "dur": "3.107", 
            "start": "478.654"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It felt like a real compliment\nto my teachings.", 
            "dur": "2.821", 
            "start": "481.761"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "My message of love and be loved\nwas really making an impact.", 
            "dur": "4.198", 
            "start": "484.582"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "For years, I&#39;ve been practicing", 
            "dur": "1.705", 
            "start": "489.51"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "shouting commands\nfor the NFL football field,", 
            "dur": "3.768", 
            "start": "491.215"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but I had been practicing\nanother message all along.", 
            "dur": "4.561", 
            "start": "494.983"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I was never the type of football player\nthat was overly aggressive or tough.", 
            "dur": "5.238", 
            "start": "500.494"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I never yelled at my teammates,", 
            "dur": "2.417", 
            "start": "506.692"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and I never yell\nat my students in the classroom.", 
            "dur": "2.948", 
            "start": "509.109"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Some people say this may make\npeople walk all over you,", 
            "dur": "5.082", 
            "start": "512.986"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but I believe otherwise.", 
            "dur": "1.774", 
            "start": "518.748"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "An older teacher once told me,\nwhen I first began teaching,", 
            "dur": "4.549", 
            "start": "521.611"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that I shouldn&#39;t smile in the classroom\nuntil after a few months have gone by.", 
            "dur": "3.87", 
            "start": "526.98"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "(Laughter)", 
            "dur": "1.115", 
            "start": "530.858"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I guess the theory is that the students\nwould think I was tough,", 
            "dur": "3.532", 
            "start": "531.989"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but I love to smile,", 
            "dur": "2.425", 
            "start": "535.521"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and I have a different theory.", 
            "dur": "1.854", 
            "start": "537.946"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I believe that \nthe toughest guy in the room", 
            "dur": "4.873", 
            "start": "540.65"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "is not the football guy;", 
            "dur": "1.723", 
            "start": "545.523"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "it&#39;s the loving guy.", 
            "dur": "1.774", 
            "start": "548.266"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s the most manly thing\nthat can ever be accomplished.", 
            "dur": "4.234", 
            "start": "551.19"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s not that difficult to do,", 
            "dur": "2.667", 
            "start": "556.144"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but it requires great thought and courage.", 
            "dur": "4.515", 
            "start": "558.811"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I loved football because I thought\nit was one of the finest team sports.", 
            "dur": "4.447", 
            "start": "564.626"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "When we&#39;re on the field,", 
            "dur": "1.587", 
            "start": "569.073"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "playing together, relating as teammates,", 
            "dur": "3.176", 
            "start": "570.66"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "defending each other,\nprotecting each other,", 
            "dur": "2.659", 
            "start": "573.836"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "doing a little dance in the end zone\nto celebrate the points we score -", 
            "dur": "3.618", 
            "start": "576.495"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Football was really about relationships.", 
            "dur": "2.67", 
            "start": "580.113"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And so is love.", 
            "dur": "1.654", 
            "start": "583.613"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Love is a team sport.", 
            "dur": "1.936", 
            "start": "586.747"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "A team that we are all a part of.", 
            "dur": "2.804", 
            "start": "589.953"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And on this team, Daniel is an all-star.", 
            "dur": "4.31", 
            "start": "593.477"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But Daniel never had\nthe glory of an end zone dance,", 
            "dur": "4.652", 
            "start": "598.667"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "or even a dance at his junior prom.", 
            "dur": "2.688", 
            "start": "603.319"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And that&#39;s because his life\nextinguished way too early.", 
            "dur": "2.83", 
            "start": "607.037"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "One night, during Daniel&#39;s junior year,", 
            "dur": "3.75", 
            "start": "610.557"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "in February,", 
            "dur": "2.014", 
            "start": "614.307"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "he was rolling up the mats\nwith his wrestling buddies,", 
            "dur": "2.875", 
            "start": "616.321"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and he collapsed in pain.", 
            "dur": "1.745", 
            "start": "619.196"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Daniel suffered an aortic aneurysm,", 
            "dur": "4.046", 
            "start": "621.631"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and he died\nearly the next morning in hospital.", 
            "dur": "2.598", 
            "start": "625.677"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It was tragic.", 
            "dur": "1.439", 
            "start": "629.395"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The date was February 7th, 2002.", 
            "dur": "4.812", 
            "start": "631.994"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Exactly 12 years ago today.", 
            "dur": "2.675", 
            "start": "638.136"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I don&#39;t think it&#39;s any coincidence\nthat I&#39;m here today with the opportunity", 
            "dur": "4.393", 
            "start": "642.351"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to share Daniel&#39;s story with you.", 
            "dur": "3.002", 
            "start": "646.744"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Daniel is my lighthouse.", 
            "dur": "2.874", 
            "start": "651.186"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "When the water is dark and dangerous,", 
            "dur": "3.758", 
            "start": "655.3"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the lighthouse can provide\na warm and inviting light,", 
            "dur": "4.218", 
            "start": "659.058"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "almost as if to say, this way home.", 
            "dur": "3.602", 
            "start": "663.276"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Daniel brought me home\nliterally by bringing me to his home.", 
            "dur": "4.618", 
            "start": "668.448"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The night after he died,\nI visited his family,", 
            "dur": "3.124", 
            "start": "674.536"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "along with the number \nof other teachers from our school.", 
            "dur": "3.411", 
            "start": "677.66"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "We were all greeted\nby Daniel&#39;s cousin Lia,", 
            "dur": "3.71", 
            "start": "682.001"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "who thanked us for being there\nduring such a devastating time.", 
            "dur": "4.468", 
            "start": "686.701"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I introduced myself\nas Daniel&#39;s theology teacher,", 
            "dur": "3.563", 
            "start": "692.709"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and she replied,", 
            "dur": "1.649", 
            "start": "696.272"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "&quot;Oh, you&#39;re the one\nthat Daniel wanted me to marry!&quot;", 
            "dur": "3.282", 
            "start": "698.621"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "(Laughter)", 
            "dur": "1.311", 
            "start": "701.903"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It was kind of like a light went on.", 
            "dur": "2.37", 
            "start": "703.214"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I ended up sitting with Lia and her mom,", 
            "dur": "3.056", 
            "start": "706.424"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "sharing stories of Daniel\nand looking at pictures.", 
            "dur": "3.272", 
            "start": "710.17"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It was a really difficult time\nfor us both,", 
            "dur": "3.233", 
            "start": "714.332"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but it hard for me not to notice", 
            "dur": "2.808", 
            "start": "717.565"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that Lia had the same passion\nand energy for life", 
            "dur": "4.085", 
            "start": "720.373"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that I saw in Daniel.", 
            "dur": "1.713", 
            "start": "724.458"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I wish he could have seen us meet.", 
            "dur": "2.636", 
            "start": "727.101"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Riding home that night, I quietly recalled\nmy last moment with Daniel.", 
            "dur": "5.073", 
            "start": "730.709"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "He was visiting my class.", 
            "dur": "1.825", 
            "start": "737.592"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And like many times before,", 
            "dur": "1.949", 
            "start": "741.747"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Daniel would just stroll right in.", 
            "dur": "2.101", 
            "start": "744.496"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And because I was sitting behind the desk,\nhe came over to me,", 
            "dur": "2.965", 
            "start": "746.607"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and we&#39;re about the same height,", 
            "dur": "1.619", 
            "start": "749.572"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and our shoulders bumped\ninto each other as we talked.", 
            "dur": "2.838", 
            "start": "751.191"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I introduced him to the class", 
            "dur": "1.43", 
            "start": "754.029"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "as the 103-pound wrestler\nwho was having a great season,", 
            "dur": "3.698", 
            "start": "755.459"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and the younger guys\njust looked at him in awe.", 
            "dur": "2.487", 
            "start": "759.157"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Here was this guy,\nsmaller than most of them,", 
            "dur": "3.087", 
            "start": "762.664"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but he carried so much weight\nand loving energy.", 
            "dur": "3.457", 
            "start": "765.751"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "On his way out \nof the classroom that morning,", 
            "dur": "2.146", 
            "start": "769.208"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Daniel turned over his shoulder\nin his cool little way and said,", 
            "dur": "3.723", 
            "start": "771.354"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "&quot;See you around, Mr. Ward.&quot;", 
            "dur": "2.432", 
            "start": "775.077"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Daniel died early the next morning.", 
            "dur": "2.534", 
            "start": "778.539"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Couple of weeks later,\nI thought I saw Daniel at school.", 
            "dur": "4.092", 
            "start": "782.173"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The student was sitting\nwith [his] back to me,", 
            "dur": "2.994", 
            "start": "787.185"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and it looked like Daniel.", 
            "dur": "2.145", 
            "start": "790.179"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And for a moment\nI believed that it was him.", 
            "dur": "2.999", 
            "start": "793.264"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But soon the student stood,\nand it obviously wasn&#39;t Daniel.", 
            "dur": "3.686", 
            "start": "797.673"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But to me the message was clear.", 
            "dur": "3.759", 
            "start": "802.859"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The same love and light", 
            "dur": "2.473", 
            "start": "808.138"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that I witnessed \nand experienced in Daniel,", 
            "dur": "3.372", 
            "start": "810.611"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "could be found in everyone and everything.", 
            "dur": "4.326", 
            "start": "813.983"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So I began to look for Daniel,", 
            "dur": "2.247", 
            "start": "819.009"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to look for love\nin everyone and everything,", 
            "dur": "3.216", 
            "start": "821.256"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and at the crucial point in my life,\neven in myself.", 
            "dur": "3.315", 
            "start": "824.472"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Daniel was right when he said,\n&quot;See you around.&quot;", 
            "dur": "3.665", 
            "start": "828.847"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Because the same love in him\nis within us all.", 
            "dur": "4.287", 
            "start": "833.252"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Just as I tell my students back at school,", 
            "dur": "3.035", 
            "start": "838.669"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "there is so much goodness in you,", 
            "dur": "3.566", 
            "start": "841.704"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and you are all, each and everyone of you,", 
            "dur": "3.752", 
            "start": "845.27"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "worthy of love and belonging,", 
            "dur": "3.238", 
            "start": "849.022"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "just as you are, imperfectly perfect.", 
            "dur": "3.748", 
            "start": "852.26"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And once you begin open yourself to love,", 
            "dur": "3.369", 
            "start": "856.768"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "you will learn to see it everywhere,", 
            "dur": "2.328", 
            "start": "860.137"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "creating a peace, a freedom and a truth", 
            "dur": "5.169", 
            "start": "862.465"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that will shift your overall,\nentire experience.", 
            "dur": "2.826", 
            "start": "867.634"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Think about it.", 
            "dur": "1.286", 
            "start": "871.17"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "If I stand right here\nand I shift just a little bit,", 
            "dur": "4.834", 
            "start": "872.456"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "my view changes entirely.", 
            "dur": "2.085", 
            "start": "877.94"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The same is true for love.", 
            "dur": "2.112", 
            "start": "880.905"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "If we can begin to make an effort", 
            "dur": "2.345", 
            "start": "883.017"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to love and be loved\nwithout any conditions,", 
            "dur": "3.741", 
            "start": "885.362"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "we will bring a whole new level of meaning", 
            "dur": "2.595", 
            "start": "889.103"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to our relationships\nand to our experience.", 
            "dur": "3.719", 
            "start": "891.698"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I&#39;m going to ask you\nto close your eyes one more time.", 
            "dur": "2.956", 
            "start": "896.447"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Picture the sun.", 
            "dur": "1.408", 
            "start": "900.353"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Author Anthony de Mello writes:", 
            "dur": "2.545", 
            "start": "902.971"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "&quot;Has the Sun ever said\nto the Earth: you owe me.", 
            "dur": "5.405", 
            "start": "905.516"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Look what happens to a love like that.\nIt lights up the whole sky.&quot;", 
            "dur": "5.207", 
            "start": "911.591"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Is there somebody in your life\nthat can use a little unconditional love?", 
            "dur": "4.123", 
            "start": "917.498"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Picture that person now.", 
            "dur": "2.168", 
            "start": "921.621"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Remember the lighthouse.", 
            "dur": "2.251", 
            "start": "925.759"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Remember its primary purpose:\nTo help guide sailors and boaters home.", 
            "dur": "5.505", 
            "start": "928.01"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Is there somebody in your life\nthat can use a little guidance,", 
            "dur": "4.203", 
            "start": "934.595"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "a little direction?", 
            "dur": "1.34", 
            "start": "938.798"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Picture that person now.", 
            "dur": "1.77", 
            "start": "940.798"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And, lastly, picture the disco ball.", 
            "dur": "2.513", 
            "start": "944.768"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Daniel was free to be himself", 
            "dur": "3.255", 
            "start": "948.631"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "because he loved himself unconditionally.", 
            "dur": "3.024", 
            "start": "951.886"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "We could all reflect \na little bit of love back home,", 
            "dur": "4.683", 
            "start": "956.27"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "so that we can dance\nlike nobody is watching.", 
            "dur": "2.959", 
            "start": "960.953"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Is there something in your life\nthat you&#39;ve been waiting to do?", 
            "dur": "3.551", 
            "start": "964.612"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Gently float open your eyes and smile.", 
            "dur": "3.835", 
            "start": "970.053"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Twelve years ago, after Daniel died,", 
            "dur": "3.651", 
            "start": "975.128"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I decided to ask his cousin Lia out\nfor dinner in his honor.", 
            "dur": "4.726", 
            "start": "980.269"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "We had so much to talk about,", 
            "dur": "3.758", 
            "start": "986.365"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and I&#39;m happy to tell you that,\nfour years after that,", 
            "dur": "4.555", 
            "start": "991.323"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I asked Lia to marry me.", 
            "dur": "2.264", 
            "start": "996.728"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "She continues\nto light up my life every day,", 
            "dur": "3.416", 
            "start": "1000.272"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Lia is my sunshine,\nand now we have two sons.", 
            "dur": "3.803", 
            "start": "1003.688"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Our oldest is almost three,\nand his name is John Daniel,", 
            "dur": "4.476", 
            "start": "1008.521"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "whom we affectionately call J.D.,", 
            "dur": "2.775", 
            "start": "1013.967"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and he&#39;s our little disco ball.", 
            "dur": "2.022", 
            "start": "1016.742"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "We also have another son,\nwho is just 12 weeks old now.", 
            "dur": "3.168", 
            "start": "1019.394"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "His name is Casey Christian,\nand he&#39;s our little lighthouse.", 
            "dur": "4.414", 
            "start": "1023.142"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "When people ask Lia", 
            "dur": "1.914", 
            "start": "1028.626"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "if the boys will play football in the NFL\nsomeday like their daddy did,", 
            "dur": "4.59", 
            "start": "1031.56"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "she says, &quot;Maybe.&quot;", 
            "dur": "2.539", 
            "start": "1036.8"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But our only wish for them\nis to truly live a life", 
            "dur": "5.238", 
            "start": "1040.56"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "where they can love and be loved.", 
            "dur": "3.344", 
            "start": "1045.798"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Thank you very much.", 
            "dur": "1.482", 
            "start": "1049.782"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "(Applause)", 
            "dur": "2.267", 
            "start": "1051.264"
        }
    ], 
